// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0799 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: bcf66cb4-1f4e-54a3-9d02-e596a63cd423

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.10*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:13.10*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*")
